Argentina, November 29-December 25. All games played in Buenos Aires. Chile and Uruguay withdrew, Chile because of the bad performance one year ago, and Uruguay because of conflicts inside the Association. This renounces forced the organizers to modify the schedule. Finally the championship was played in two rounds.

29.11.25  Buenos Aires, Boca Juniors

ARG - PAR 2:0 (1:0)

(18,000) Ricardo Vallarino URU

